statements: SELECT * FROM real_estate_assets;
SELECT asset_id, location, asset_type FROM real_estate_assets WHERE num_bedrooms = 3;
SELECT * FROM real_estate_assets WHERE location = 'New York';
SELECT asset_id, num_bedrooms, num_bathrooms FROM real_estate_assets ORDER BY num_bedrooms DESC;
SELECT location, COUNT(asset_id) AS num_assets FROM real_estate_assets GROUP BY location HAVING COUNT(asset_id) > 1;
SELECT * FROM real_estate_assets WHERE num_bedrooms > 3;
SELECT location, asset_type FROM real_estate_assets WHERE num_bathrooms = 2;
SELECT asset_id, location, num_bedrooms FROM real_estate_assets WHERE asset_type = 'House' ORDER BY num_bedrooms DESC;
SELECT * FROM real_estate_assets WHERE num_bedrooms < 2 AND num_bathrooms > 1;
SELECT asset_id, location, asset_type, num_bedrooms, num_bathrooms FROM real_estate_assets WHERE location LIKE '%New York%' ORDER BY asset_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM Location WHERE city = 'New York';
SELECT id, address FROM Location WHERE country = 'USA';
SELECT * FROM AssetSpecs WHERE price > 100000 ORDER BY bedrooms DESC;
SELECT id, bedrooms, bathrooms FROM AssetSpecs WHERE area_sqft > 2000 ORDER BY price ASC;
SELECT city, state, country FROM Location WHERE country = 'Canada';
SELECT * FROM Location WHERE city='New York' AND state='NY' ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT address, city, state, country FROM Location WHERE country='USA' AND state='CA' ORDER BY address ASC;
SELECT id, asset_type, price FROM AssetSpecs WHERE price > 100000 ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT * FROM AssetSpecs WHERE bedrooms >= 2 AND bathrooms >= 2 ORDER BY area_sqft DESC, bedrooms ASC;
SELECT id, asset_type, area_sqft, price FROM AssetSpecs WHERE area_sqft BETWEEN 1000 AND 2000 AND price < 500000 ORDER BY id ASC;
SELECT * FROM RealEstateAsset;
SELECT asset_id, location FROM RealEstateAsset WHERE asset_id = 1;
SELECT owner_id, asset_id, owner_name FROM AssetOwner WHERE owner_name LIKE 'John%';
SELECT * FROM AssetHistory ORDER BY change_date DESC;
SELECT asset_id, COUNT(history_id) AS total_changes FROM AssetHistory GROUP BY asset_id HAVING COUNT(history_id) > 2;
SELECT * FROM RealEstateAsset WHERE asset_id = 1;
SELECT location, specifications FROM RealEstateAsset;
SELECT owner_name, owner_contact FROM AssetOwner WHERE owner_id = 2;
SELECT a.asset_id, a.location, ah.change_date FROM RealEstateAsset a JOIN AssetHistory ah ON a.asset_id = ah.asset_id;
SELECT ah.history_id, ah.asset_id, ah.change_date, r.location FROM AssetHistory ah JOIN RealEstateAsset r ON ah.asset_id = r.asset_id WHERE ah.change_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM real_estate_assets;

SELECT asset_id, AVG(rating) AS avg_rating FROM asset_ratings GROUP BY asset_id;

SELECT MAX(size_sqft), MIN(price), AVG(rating) FROM real_estate_assets JOIN asset_ratings ON real_estate_assets.asset_id = asset_ratings.asset_id;

SELECT location, build_year, price, COUNT(*) AS total_ratings FROM real_estjsonate_assets JOIN asset_ratings ON real_estjsonate_assets.asset_id = asset_ratings.asset_id GROUP BY location, build_year, price;
